name: Movement
description:
Blessed movement that has left me restless, that allows me to inhabit other moments. I am not an expert in generative art, but I love its expression, pure, simple. This piece is a little piece of me now, that simple, loud, colorful and creepy.

What do I say when I'm not moving? How do I know that I am moving? How do I transfer information from my body to others bodies?
